  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\r\nI recently wanted a way to restrict function calls for each user by some time. That's when I was searching if there was a utils contract in OpenZeppelin contracts, but I didn't find one. So I decided to make one and contribute here.\r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\nI have created a repo with the contract and documentation on how to use it. You can find the repo [here](https://github.com/RedHeadphone/CallRestrict). I've added tests to verify the logic of smart contract. I would like to know your opinions and suggestions (if any) on this util contract. If everything looks good, I can make PR adding Call Restrict.\r\n",
